25 SECTION 3. IC 13-18-10-2.4 IS ADDED TO THE INDIANA
26 CODE AS A NEW SECTION TO READ AS FOLLOWS
27 [EFFECTIVE JULY 1, 2026]: Sec. 2.4. (a) Except as provided in
28 subsection (b), an applicant that applies for approval under section
29 1 of this chapter is not required to design or install one (1) or more
30 of the following for solid manure produced from livestock on straw
31 pack or dry pack bedding:
32 (1) Manure pumps.
33 (2) Flush systems.
34 (3) Slatted floors and gutter systems.
35 (4) Similar devices.
36 (b) If the straw pack or dry pack bedding is:
37 (1) placed over a concrete manure storage pit; or
38 (2) connected to a flush system;
39 then the applicant must install at least one (1) of the items
40 described in subsection (a).
41 SECTION 4. IC 13-18-10-2.8 IS ADDED TO THE INDIANA
42 CODE AS A NEW SECTION TO READ AS FOLLOWS
